---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Síntesis del Paradigma Cibernético - Marco Sintético">
  <!-- Title Section -->
  <header class="w-full max-w-7xl pt-8 pb-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center animate-fade-in">
    <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed text-on-primary-fixed text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Paradigma Cibernético</span>
    <h1 class="font-headline font-extrabold text-3xl md:text-5xl text-primary tracking-tight mb-2 uppercase">
      Síntesis del Paradigma Cibernético
    </h1>
    <span class="text-tertiary opacity-50 text-lg md:text-2xl font-light mb-4">(Natural - Artificial)</span>
    <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">
      Visualización de la convergencia técnica entre sistemas orgánicos y arquitecturas artificiales de transferencia.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Main Diagram -->
  <main class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 pb-12">
    <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
      <!-- SVG Background -->
      <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none hidden lg:block -z-10" fill="none" viewbox="0 0 1200 600" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path class="opacity-40 animate-flow" d="M300 300 C 450 150, 750 150, 900 300" stroke="url(#gradient-flow)" stroke-dasharray="8 8" stroke-width="2"></path>
        <path class="opacity-40 animate-flow" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;" d="M300 300 C 450 450, 750 450, 900 300" stroke="url(#gradient-flow)" stroke-dasharray="8 8" stroke-width="2"></path>
        <defs>
        <linearGradient id="gradient-flow" x1="0%" x2="100%" y1="0%" y2="0%">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#00472f"></stop>
        <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#9b4500"></stop>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#303e52"></stop>
        </linearGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>

      <!-- Left: TECNOLOGÍA PROPIA -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 z-10 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-primary"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-primary tracking-tight">Tecnología Propia</h2>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-container opacity-40 text-3xl md:text-4xl">agriculture</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-4 md:mb-6 bg-surface-container">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" alt="Agricultura técnica" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuB-R0C9mA3VchL9lr7mwrQQoqDND5LwxvF6wMBmdOfAUQTSHEUb8eEO0pw0v1T1cy8slDXPcOqLxOZrWX_j7CMuYomNY-kMjNhAfc5aFDAQwgIxtyOUS4tKAj_RR1uwYERBjGuGGv7QKuIYsVHx1YxjyLaHPVtCE8dlJwuKWMH7bbU2Nz7vZEMM-1hwSc6-EhXpGwpKzek0ca7YOZzLK9LtFkHUVnCMarBClwg9nGuvRyZPDZTZoLUpEy9hlHuLLCJrLq4lvnpeye3N"/>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm mt-1">schema</span>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Apropiación Privática</p>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-medium">Información de la manera (Sistemas Naturales).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 md:p-3 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg text-[9px] md:text-[10px] text-primary/70 font-mono italic">
              // Input: Ciclos Biológicos<br/>
              // Protocolo: Adaptación Vernácula
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Center: CENTRO DE SÍNTESIS -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 z-20 flex flex-col items-center animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.4s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-square flex items-center justify-center max-w-[250px] md:max-w-[300px]">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-4 border-dashed border-secondary/20 animate-spin-slow" style="animation: spin 60s linear infinite;"></div>
          <div class="glass-panel w-40 h-40 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-4 md:p-8 shadow-2xl border border-secondary-container/30 relative">
            <div class="absolute -top-4 px-2 md:px-4 py-1 bg-secondary text-white text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full tracking-tighter">Centro de Síntesis</div>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-2 md:mb-4" style="font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">hub</span>
            <h3 class="font-headline font-extrabold text-sm md:text-lg text-secondary leading-tight uppercase">Tecnología Punta Propia</h3>
            <p class="text-[8px] md:text-[11px] text-on-secondary-fixed-variant font-bold mt-1 md:mt-2 opacity-70 tracking-widest">(Software de la manera)</p>
            <div class="mt-2 md:mt-4 flex gap-1">
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-secondary"></div>
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-secondary opacity-50"></div>
              <div class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-secondary opacity-25"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-8 md:-top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center">
            <span class="text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-1 md:mb-2">Transferencia</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary animate-bounce text-lg md:text-2xl">arrow_downward</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: TECNOLOGÍA TRANSFERIDA -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-4 z-10 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s; opacity: 0;">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all border border-outline-variant/10 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1.5 h-full bg-tertiary"></div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
            <h2 class="font-headline font-bold text-lg md:text-xl text-tertiary tracking-tight">Tecnología Transferida</h2>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container opacity-40 text-3xl md:text-4xl">satellite_alt</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-4 md:mb-6 bg-surface-container">
            <img class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" alt="Satélite digital" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD1oTB2QDHWwnRQwFqkhojXGxUo6SR4qY12caJH5nCTWZ8n-_j2aNXrgitMQ8fTM0LuJjdNrNxCBph1LuKOnRhAoi12IFeAZUu9fIg1TWiExA9oAZ4lAxtxfEtME4VJeceJCVc7wZ1OmYRwGY54a5OS9yDwVXUwbwe7Nx99glklu6NE7Bb-Zpct6ehJYp4a5mHi-9rSzOwVAUVHsQr6z3vtmGyRhUi2DUIBacjUe5sEvxvLFxZQbBmR_uHBozOa-IYy0_JgbmHDS5xc"/>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-sm mt-1">biotech</span>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-bold text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Paradigma de Punta</p>
                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-medium">Información Artificial (Sistemas Digitales).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-2 md:p-3 bg-surface-container-low rounded-lg text-[9px] md:text-[10px] text-tertiary/70 font-mono italic">
              // Output: Eficiencia de Escala<br/>
              // Protocolo: Interoperabilidad Global
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Technical Note Section -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 mb-16 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s; opacity: 0;">
    <div class="bg-surface-container-low rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-10 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 opacity-10 p-4">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[80px] md:text-[120px] text-primary">data_object</span>
      </div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
        <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">description</span>
          Nota Técnica sobre la Síntesis
        </h4>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          La convergencia entre el paradigma natural y el artificial no representa una sustitución, sino una <span class="text-secondary font-bold">simbiosis operacional</span>. El "Software de la manera" actúa como el traductor cibernético que permite que la apropiación de la información natural sea procesada bajo estándares de tecnología de punta, resultando en un ecosistema de productividad social optimizado y resiliente.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 md:mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3 md:gap-4">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-bold text-tertiary uppercase">Ratio: 0.94</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-bold text-tertiary uppercase">Latencia: &lt; 2ms</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white border border-outline-variant/20 rounded-lg text-[8px] md:text-[10px] font-bold text-tertiary uppercase">Protocolo: Natural-Link v4.0</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Navegación -->
  <div class="flex justify-between mt-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <a href="/gestion-social" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
      Anterior
    </a>
  </div>

  <style>
    .glass-panel {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
